# First Week Scripts

## Post Templates

### Pain Post

```text
[Niche] owners often think the problem is no traffic.

But many stores already get some views. The real leak is usually:
1. the post does not lead to a clear appointment action
2. the DM reply only gives a price
3. the package price does not show value

I made a simple [sample/tool] to check this.
Comment "[keyword]" and I will send it.
```

### Template Demo Post

```text
I organized a [niche] 30-day content calendar.

Each row includes:
- post angle
- title
- shooting idea
- customer pain
- CTA

This is for [target customer], not for people who already have a full marketing team.
Comment "[keyword]" for the free sample.
```

### Pricing Post

```text
If you sell a service package but do not calculate labor, material, platform cost, and refund risk, the order may look profitable but lose money.

I made a simple pricing calculator for [niche].

It shows:
- minimum profitable price
- gross margin
- discount limit
- follow-up status

Comment "[keyword]" for the sample.
```

## DM Scripts

### Send Sample

```text
Here is the sample.

It is a small version of the full toolkit. You can try it today.

Which part is more urgent for you right now: traffic, inquiry conversion, pricing, or customer follow-up?
```

### Qualify Lead

```text
Got it. That sounds like a [pain type] problem.

How are you solving it now? Are you using a spreadsheet, handwritten notes, WeChat tags, or nothing systematic yet?
```

### Present Product

```text
The full toolkit may fit your case.

It includes:
- 30-day content calendar
- DM reply templates
- package pricing calculator
- lead tracker
- walkthrough video

Basic is [price]. Pro is [price] and includes examples and updates.

I can send the directory and screenshots first.
```

### Follow Up

```text
Did you get a chance to try the sample?

If you only use one part today, I recommend starting with [specific part]. It usually shows the fastest result.
```

### Upsell Service

```text
If you want, I can help adapt the toolkit to your store/business.

The setup package includes:
- customizing the first 10 content ideas
- rewriting 5 DM replies
- checking 3 package prices
- setting up the lead tracker

The price is [price], and delivery takes [time].
```

